latestIgtvVideos.title: Y/PROJECT X FILA SS22
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The 110th anniversary, for FILA, is the occasion to celebrate the innovative and daring spirit of the brand with unexpected collaborations that propel the action one step further. The next one is Y/PROJECT.
A marriage of two identities, resulting in a unique collection.
There is not one single way to own an item: everything is possible, and independent interpretations are welcome.

CREDITS
A film by Grégoire Dyer
Styled by Robbie Spencer
Produced by Division
Director of photography Bernard Jallet
Set design by Céline Corbineau
Music by Senjan Jansen 
Casting by Oliver Ress & Emmanuelle Delserieys at Creartvt 
Make-up by Carole Colombani with L'oreal Paris products
Hair by Ramona Eschbach with L'oreal Paris products

latestIgtvVideos.title: FILA 110th Anniversary
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
As a part of the #FILA110 Anniversary, FILA teamed up with @kegrand to present the FILA 110th Anniversary Collection at Milano Fashion Week @cameramoda 🌎

The 110th anniversary collection is a celebration of FILA’s iconic heritage through the eyes of stylist, creative director and cultural curator Katie Grand @kegrand.

Directed by @steve_mackey, @kegrand collection is presented through video game graphics, powerful neon & fluroscent colours and the classic red, white and blue of #FILA bursting on the walls. After exploring the whole of FILA’s collection each piece selected was chosen for their historical value and beauty but reissued and redesigned with a modern update. Discover the #FILA110 ❣️

Creative director and stylist @kegrand
Director @steve__mackey
